      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BANDIT LYNNE (6) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in three starts, including two wins. Recorded a 3.5 lengths win (29.57) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Expected to be in the finish. STATUS JEWEL (4) won again in another strong performance after running them ragged to bring up five wins in a row, scoring by 2.5 lengths (29.81) at this track over 520m. Sure to be thereabouts. ERUPT (1) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 1.75 lengths at this track in a handy 29.65 beating GALBA MODEL. Has performed well from this box with a win and four minor placings to her name from nine starts. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. KUNG FU ETHICS (2) can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
